data.description: Your Dream Pool Home Oasis awaits with low $45 Electric Bills in Summer months in North Port Estates on half acre. 4 bedroom with 3 full baths for possible In Law Suite.  The Best deal is the Solar Panels a $70,000 value. This impeccably designed residence, built in 2018, boasts over 2350 square feet of luxurious living space on a spacious half-acre lot. Step inside to discover an open-concept floor plan flooded with natural light, creating a welcoming ambiance throughout. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with high-end appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. The expansive living area seamlessly connects to a dining space, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories.  With four bedrooms, this home offers flexibility and comfort for both daily living and entertaining. The master suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring a spa-like bathroom and a walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms provide versatility, ideal for a home office or guest accommodations.  Venture outside to your private retreat. The backyard, situated on over half an acre, has been meticulously landscaped to provide both privacy and tranquility. The sparkling pool invites you to enjoy the Florida sunshine, creating the perfect setting for outdoor living.  What sets this property apart is a remarkable $70,000 solar upgrade, seamlessly integrated to harness the power of the sun. This cutting-edge feature not only reduces energy costs but also minimizes your carbon footprint, making this home an environmentally conscious choice.  Located in the desirable North Port area, this home offers a serene neighborhood setting while being conveniently close to amenities, schools, and recreational opportunities. Easy access to major highways means you're just a short drive away from the Gulf Coast's beautiful beaches, shopping, dining, and entertainment.  This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle choice. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in this 2018-built home with a $70,000 solar upgrade, a pool, and over half an acre in North Port!
